Privacy Policy and Terms of Use
By using Audify Music Player, you consent to have read, understood, and agree to our “Privacy Policy” and “Terms of Use” provided herein.
You are a valued user and respecting your privacy is our major concern. We do not collect any personally identifiable information. We do not process your personal information or disseminate it to Third Parties for any reason whatsoever except as provided under Section 5 of this agreement. The information collected by us is mainly to generate logs, error reports, performance log analytics reports, crash reports,
etc
. which does not identify you personally. This information is needed to let you have the best experience with the Application. We do not sell or trade upon your data.
